      "code": "# Let's search quran for verses containing both \"اخذ\" and \"بني اسرائيل\" after normalization\ndef norm_contains(s, kw):\n    return normalize_ar(s).find(kw) != -1\n\ntargets = []\nfor entry in quran_data:\n    text = entry['ayah_text']\n    norm = normalize_ar(text)\n    if 'اخذ' in norm and 'بني اسرائيل' in norm:\n        targets.append((entry, norm))\n        \nlen(targets)",
