      "code": "def contains_all(norm, substrings):\n    return all(sub in norm for sub in substrings)\n\n# We'll search for \"اخذ\" and \"بني\" and \"اسرا\"\ncands = []\nfor entry in quran_data:\n    norm = normalize_ar(entry['ayah_text'])\n    if contains_all(norm, ['اخذ', 'بني', 'اسرا']):\n        cands.append((entry, norm))\nlen(cands)",
